---
description: Repo-wide architecture and maintainability rules
globs:
  - "**/*"
alwaysApply: true
---

- Keep files and functions small; avoid huge components and broad utility modules.
- Separate UI, API boundaries, deterministic security logic, and OpenAI narrative generation.
- Keep API payloads typed and stable.
- Never expose secrets to the frontend or commit `.env`.
- Ask before adding new production dependencies.
- Run available lint, build, and tests after changes.
